data.description: This classic 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom tri-level home sits on 2.66 wooded acres, offering a blend of tranquility and convenience. Step inside to discover an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The heart of the home boasts a spacious well-equipped kitchen. Picture yourself hosting gatherings or drinking your morning coffee in this welcoming space or on the expansive decks overlooking the backyard and above ground pool. The home exudes a timeless appeal, ready for your personal touches. Conveniently located next to commuter ways, this residence offers easy access to the hustle and bustle of life and a serene place to return to. Imagine the convenience of being close to amenities yet coming home to a peaceful sanctuary every day.
